{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_MON_240.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong? You don't look very happy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I was just concerned about something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Concerned about what?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You remember the other day, when we talked about singing at the shop?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I would have felt really bad if I did nothing, so I helped out a little with the concert."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I heard from Mr. Horst. I heard Tess had an... Amazing performance..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes, she seemed to be having a lot of fun..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Although her singing was, um... I don't think it's something suited for most people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But Tess didn't seem to mind at all, and she just continued to have fun singing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "The guests seemed to be having fun too because of that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "When I saw Tess like that, I started to feel a little envious..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Envious...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I really like singing. So I was always worried about what people thought of my singing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "You're really worried about that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Leon. Why are you here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I had some business in the area. But that doesn't matter right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Anyway Monika, so you're worried about what people think of your singing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yes. It would only be natural to worry about what the people listening to you think."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "It's true that even when I make clothes, I think about the people who see it and wear it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "But I'd still make clothes, even if nobody appreciated what I made."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "What?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "That's because I want to make clothes. I would never give up, even if someone tried to stop me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "If people didn't appreciate what I made, I'd work harder so they would learn to appreciate it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Leon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "You have someone right here who's saying they want to hear you sing. What's there to worry about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "...You're right, there's people who want to hear me. I want to sing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I want to make everyone smile with my singing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "That's the spirit. I'm cheering for you too. Anyway, I have to get back to business, I'll be going now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "See you two later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Y-yeah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Now that that's decided, I need to go convince my parents!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "...You really are serious about everything, Monika."
        }
    ]
}